00:34:14.440 --> 00:34:15.199
feelings

00:34:15.840 --> 00:34:17.239
cannot grow.

00:34:20.920 --> 00:34:22.159
But she's my mom.

00:34:24.039 --> 00:34:26.039
She's my closest blood relative.

00:34:30.800 --> 00:34:34.480
But time and memories make family family,

00:34:34.960 --> 00:34:35.880
not blood.

00:34:36.440 --> 00:34:37.079
Besides,

00:34:38.119 --> 00:34:39.639
as long as you haven't forgotten Auntie,

00:34:40.280 --> 00:34:41.199
those memories

00:34:41.639 --> 00:34:42.639
won't disappear.

00:34:43.360 --> 00:34:43.880
Right?

00:35:05.960 --> 00:35:06.920
What did my mom say?

00:35:08.079 --> 00:35:08.719
Nothing much.

00:35:09.280 --> 00:35:11.000
I saw it. Hurry up and tell me.

00:35:13.599 --> 00:35:14.199
Don't look.

00:35:14.199 --> 00:35:15.360
Come on. Don't make me get physical.

00:35:17.039 --> 00:35:17.960
You asked to see it.

00:35:18.559 --> 00:35:19.440
Hurry up.

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:22.119
What did she send?

00:35:22.840 --> 00:35:23.840
Rui Rui,

00:35:24.119 --> 00:35:26.199
don't choose a man just because he treats you well.

00:35:26.519 --> 00:35:28.480
Those who pester you aren't good news.

00:35:30.199 --> 00:35:30.760
Done reading?

00:35:32.760 --> 00:35:34.239
Didn't she just say I was reliable?

00:35:37.239 --> 00:35:39.639
You women really change your minds so fast.

00:36:07.000 --> 00:36:07.840
What's wrong, Guifang?

00:36:08.440 --> 00:36:10.000
Did I do something wrong?

00:36:10.599 --> 00:36:10.960
No.

00:36:11.760 --> 00:36:13.360
I... I just think that now you...

00:36:14.519 --> 00:36:15.400
...are quite diligent.

00:36:15.960 --> 00:36:18.280
Didn't Brother Xiaocan do any work before?

00:36:19.000 --> 00:36:20.079
I... before...

00:36:21.840 --> 00:36:22.440
...wasn't I like this?

00:36:25.320 --> 00:36:25.840
Darn it.

00:36:27.079 --> 00:36:28.840
Turns out I behaved too well.

00:36:30.960 --> 00:36:32.000
Darn it, darn it.

00:36:32.840 --> 00:36:34.320
Is she starting to suspect me?

00:36:42.079 --> 00:36:43.440
Look at this area. Here, here, here.

00:36:43.599 --> 00:36:45.320
Lush green... no, golden yellow.

00:36:46.320 --> 00:36:46.679
When the time comes...

00:36:47.320 --> 00:36:47.840
...we go from here.

00:36:48.440 --> 00:36:49.320
All the way up.

00:36:49.440 --> 00:36:51.559
Climb, climb, climb, until we reach the ridge here.

00:36:53.039 --> 00:36:53.920
And see all the mountains below.

00:36:54.239 --> 00:36:54.719
Of course...

00:36:55.199 --> 00:36:56.960
...there might be some altitude sickness.

00:36:56.960 --> 00:36:57.559
Might lack oxygen.

00:36:57.599 --> 00:36:58.039
But we...

00:36:58.039 --> 00:36:59.599
Your body now... your physique is tougher than mine.

00:36:59.639 --> 00:37:00.159
We'll just go.

00:37:00.559 --> 00:37:01.320
Or from this part.

00:37:01.760 --> 00:37:02.320
Do you see this?

00:37:03.039 --> 00:37:04.400
This... this path.

00:37:05.280 --> 00:37:06.000
That feeling...

00:37:08.159 --> 00:37:08.599
...is amazing.

00:37:09.639 --> 00:37:11.320
But to be honest, this snow mountain...

00:37:16.440 --> 00:37:16.800
Guifang.

00:37:22.559 --> 00:37:22.920
Guifang.

00:37:26.519 --> 00:37:28.519
Did you remember something?

00:37:31.360 --> 00:37:32.280
I just feel like...

00:37:33.840 --> 00:37:34.679
...I forgot a...

00:37:35.639 --> 00:37:36.320
...very...

00:37:37.039 --> 00:37:38.159
...very important thing.

00:37:46.320 --> 00:37:46.960
I'm sorry.

00:37:49.480 --> 00:37:50.480
Why are you apologizing?

00:37:51.039 --> 00:37:52.119
You didn't do anything wrong.

00:37:57.440 --> 00:37:58.719
Actually, if anyone should say it...

00:37:59.639 --> 00:38:00.960
...it should be me saying sorry.

00:38:02.199 --> 00:38:03.440
After all this time...

00:38:04.800 --> 00:38:05.800
...I just always feel...

00:38:07.079 --> 00:38:07.960
...something is a bit off.

00:38:09.960 --> 00:38:11.320
I feel we aren't really like...

00:38:11.320 --> 00:38:12.480
...a normal boyfriend and girlfriend.

00:38:14.039 --> 00:38:14.840
I don't have...

00:38:15.880 --> 00:38:16.880
...that kind of feeling for you either.

00:38:18.880 --> 00:38:20.840
I've actually wanted to say this for a long time.

00:38:22.039 --> 00:38:23.800
I feel if I don't say it now...

00:38:24.639 --> 00:38:26.880
...then I'm neither following my own heart...

00:38:27.360 --> 00:38:28.239
...nor respecting you.

00:38:30.280 --> 00:38:31.039
So, before...

00:38:31.639 --> 00:38:33.079
...no matter what happened between us...

00:38:34.079 --> 00:38:35.599
...I have to say to you today...

00:38:36.639 --> 00:38:37.159
...I'm sorry.

00:38:48.519 --> 00:38:49.760
Rejected by you again.

00:38:50.519 --> 00:38:51.119
Again?

00:38:54.039 --> 00:38:55.400
Did I reject you before?

00:38:56.159 --> 00:38:56.480
Yes.

00:39:01.400 --> 00:39:02.159
Then it seems we...

00:39:02.559 --> 00:39:03.639
...really aren't suitable.

00:39:05.840 --> 00:39:06.280
Indeed.

00:39:09.559 --> 00:39:09.960
Then...

00:39:11.440 --> 00:39:12.840
...can we still be friends?

00:39:13.639 --> 00:39:14.000
Of course.

00:39:18.880 --> 00:39:19.519
Guifang.

00:39:20.800 --> 00:39:21.679
Some things...

00:39:22.519 --> 00:39:23.719
...if you can't remember them...

00:39:25.039 --> 00:39:25.840
...maybe it's better to just forget.

00:39:29.599 --> 00:39:31.119
I feel that if there is one thing...

00:39:32.760 --> 00:39:33.920
...if I don't hurry up...

00:39:33.920 --> 00:39:34.920
...if I don't remember it...

00:39:36.119 --> 00:39:37.079
...it might be too late.

00:39:56.760 --> 00:39:58.400
What exactly did I forget?

00:40:00.360 --> 00:40:01.559
This feeling...

00:40:02.760 --> 00:40:04.719
...is like the most ordinary little thing...

00:40:05.119 --> 00:40:06.400
...has an added shadow.

00:40:08.000 --> 00:40:10.400
All happy and sad memories...

00:40:11.079 --> 00:40:12.440
...have an added gap.

00:40:14.199 --> 00:40:15.480
What exactly is it?

00:40:18.199 --> 00:40:21.199
This thing so important in your life...

00:40:21.719 --> 00:40:23.360
...yet easily lost by you.

00:40:24.880 --> 00:40:26.119
This thing that, once lost...

00:40:27.039 --> 00:40:28.719
...leaves your heart incomplete.

00:40:30.480 --> 00:40:32.079
This thing that is clearly everywhere...

00:40:33.239 --> 00:40:35.280
...yet seems nowhere to be found.

00:40:37.039 --> 00:40:38.280
What exactly is it?

00:41:07.079 --> 00:41:09.360
This is the promise between you and me

00:41:09.599 --> 00:41:10.920
Mom will help you make it happen

00:41:16.960 --> 00:41:18.079
Thank you, my wonderful mom

00:41:18.320 --> 00:41:20.679
Back home from work, after a day of labor

00:41:20.679 --> 00:41:21.519
I only love my mom

00:41:21.519 --> 00:41:23.119
You are a son's mother

00:41:23.119 --> 00:41:24.159
You are a mother

00:41:24.280 --> 00:41:25.760
Mom will definitely find a way

00:41:26.599 --> 00:41:27.199
I definitely will

00:41:27.880 --> 00:41:28.480
Mom is so good

