Mom

00:41:42.760 --> 00:41:43.559
Xiaocan

00:41:58.280 --> 00:41:59.000
I'm dying

00:41:59.000 --> 00:42:00.199
Li Wai, save me! Quick, save me!

00:42:00.199 --> 00:42:01.239
I'm dying

00:42:02.239 --> 00:42:03.159
Save me, save me

00:42:03.159 --> 00:42:03.559
Bro

00:42:04.119 --> 00:42:05.159
With me here, you won't die

00:42:05.159 --> 00:42:05.760
I'm coming

