00:42:23.920 --> 00:42:24.440
Stop playing

00:42:26.039 --> 00:42:27.000
My mom is calling me

00:42:28.480 --> 00:42:29.599
How is she calling me?

00:42:29.880 --> 00:42:30.199
She...

00:42:31.239 --> 00:42:31.639
Isn't she...

00:42:33.079 --> 00:42:33.639
