00:42:34.039 --> 00:42:34.280
No...

00:42:34.360 --> 00:42:34.760
You, quick

00:42:34.880 --> 00:42:36.119
I don't dare. How do I answer?

00:42:36.159 --> 00:42:36.639
What do I say?

00:42:36.639 --> 00:42:37.119
Answer it

00:42:40.960 --> 00:42:41.920
Hello, hi

00:42:41.920 --> 00:42:42.440
Li Wai

00:42:43.159 --> 00:42:44.400
Put Kong Xiaocan on the phone

00:42:44.679 --> 00:42:45.280
Kong Xiaocan?

00:42:45.639 --> 00:42:46.360
Who is Kong Xiaocan?

00:42:46.840 --> 00:42:47.320
Hurry up

00:42:47.440 --> 00:42:47.840
Alright

00:42:57.760 --> 00:42:58.360
Hello

00:42:58.840 --> 00:43:00.079
You're looking for me... I'm... not well

00:43:00.440 --> 00:43:01.039
Kong Xiaocan

00:43:01.199 --> 00:43:02.760
Do you plan to rot there?

00:43:02.920 --> 00:43:04.000
If you still want me as your mom

00:43:04.079 --> 00:43:05.239
Get your ass back here right now

00:43:10.400 --> 00:43:10.880
What happened?

00:43:12.480 --> 00:43:12.840
Darn it

00:44:11.239 --> 00:44:12.800
Mom, how did you remember?

00:44:22.360 --> 00:44:23.000
I was wrong

00:44:25.000 --> 00:44:26.159
I took matters into my own hands again

00:44:29.079 --> 00:44:29.719
But Mom

00:44:31.880 --> 00:44:33.440
It was the only way

00:44:36.280 --> 00:44:37.920
We've tried every trick in the book

00:44:40.039 --> 00:44:41.239
Dad left again

00:44:42.519 --> 00:44:44.400
And this isn't something money can buy

00:44:45.599 --> 00:44:46.960
Last time we went to the hospital

00:44:48.559 --> 00:44:49.559
My conscience couldn't take it

00:44:52.880 --> 00:44:53.880
This is just fate

00:44:56.360 --> 00:44:56.840
But

00:44:58.559 --> 00:44:59.360
I saw you

00:45:00.400 --> 00:45:01.840
Turn back to your old self

00:45:03.440 --> 00:45:04.400
I really had no choice

00:45:05.400 --> 00:45:05.719
I...

00:45:12.880 --> 00:45:13.840
Mom, if you're angry

00:45:14.199 --> 00:45:15.159
Just beat me up

00:45:19.800 --> 00:45:20.239
Eat

00:45:49.239 --> 00:45:49.760
Eat up.

00:45:53.719 --> 00:45:54.079
Mom.

00:45:55.079 --> 00:45:55.519
You...

00:45:58.639 --> 00:45:59.440
What were you thinking?

00:46:00.360 --> 00:46:01.320
Let me do the math for you.

00:46:02.760 --> 00:46:03.800
You kids...

00:46:04.920 --> 00:46:06.000
once you grow up,

00:46:07.599 --> 00:46:08.840
you all just want to run off.

00:46:11.559 --> 00:46:13.159
You all want to see the outside world.

00:46:15.079 --> 00:46:16.079
All year round,

00:46:16.719 --> 00:46:18.719
getting a call is like rising from the dead.

00:46:20.920 --> 00:46:22.639
You only call to ask for money.

00:46:23.480 --> 00:46:24.559
Might as well not call at all.

00:46:27.599 --> 00:46:29.400
You said you want to be a travel blogger.

00:46:31.559 --> 00:46:32.599
Then in a year,

00:46:34.440 --> 00:46:35.599
we'd only see each other

00:46:36.679 --> 00:46:38.280
for three to five days around New Year's.

00:46:41.079 --> 00:46:41.920
If you look at it that way,

00:46:43.960 --> 00:46:45.000
these twenty-one days

00:46:47.800 --> 00:46:49.920
count as spending another four or five years together.

00:46:58.480 --> 00:46:59.000
Besides,

00:47:01.679 --> 00:47:03.159
the kindness my son gave me...

00:47:04.360 --> 00:47:06.000
why shouldn't I accept it graciously?

00:47:21.159 --> 00:47:22.599
My research is on the right track now.

00:47:24.320 --> 00:47:25.960
I'll live a good life for you from now on.